{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":536,"text":"So I'll be talking about the success of my campus,"},{"time":4598,"text":"the University of Maryland, Baltimore County, UMBC,"},{"time":7348,"text":"in educating students of all types,"},{"time":10539,"text":"across the arts and humanities and the science and engineering areas."},{"time":14666,"text":"What makes our story especially important"},{"time":18744,"text":"is that we have learned so much from a group of students"},{"time":23952,"text":"who are typically not at the top of the academic ladder --"},{"time":27299,"text":"students of color, students underrepresented in selected areas."},{"time":31297,"text":"And what makes the story especially unique"},{"time":34148,"text":"is that we have learned how to help African-American students, Latino students,"},{"time":38982,"text":"students from low-income backgrounds,"},{"time":40786,"text":"to become some of the best in the world in science and engineering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44244,"text":"And so I begin with a story about my childhood."},{"time":47714,"text":"We all are products of our childhood experiences."},{"time":50786,"text":"It's hard for me to believe that it's been 50 years"},{"time":54964,"text":"since I had the experience of being a ninth grade kid in Birmingham, Alabama,"},{"time":60870,"text":"a kid who loved getting A's,"},{"time":63037,"text":"a kid who loved math, who loved to read,"},{"time":65724,"text":"a kid who would say to the teacher --"},{"time":68453,"text":"when the teacher said, \"Here are 10 problems,\" to the class,"},{"time":71709,"text":"this little fat kid would say, \"Give us 10 more.\""},{"time":75790,"text":"And the whole class would say, \"Shut up, Freeman.\""},{"time":79102,"text":"And there was a designated kicker every day."},{"time":82716,"text":"And so I was always asking this question:"},{"time":84597,"text":"\"Well how could we get more kids to really love to learn?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":90554,"text":"And amazingly, one week in church,"},{"time":93672,"text":"when I really didn't want to be there"},{"time":95754,"text":"and I was in the back of the room being placated by doing math problems,"},{"time":100855,"text":"I heard this man say this:"},{"time":103291,"text":"\"If we can get the children"},{"time":105773,"text":"to participate in this peaceful demonstration here in Birmingham,"},{"time":111770,"text":"we can show America that even children know the difference between right and wrong"},{"time":117171,"text":"and that children really do want to get the best possible education.\""},{"time":121904,"text":"And I looked up and said, \"Who is that man?\""},{"time":123625,"text":"And they said his name was Dr. Martin Luther King."},{"time":126754,"text":"And I said to my parents, \"I've got to go."},{"time":128685,"text":"I want to go. I want to be a part of this.\""},{"time":130254,"text":"And they said, \"Absolutely not.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":132124,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":133337,"text":"And we had a rough go of it."},{"time":135255,"text":"And at that time, quite frankly, you really did not talk back to your parents."},{"time":138708,"text":"And somehow I said, \"You know, you guys are hypocrites."},{"time":140995,"text":"You make me go to this. You make me listen."},{"time":142972,"text":"The man wants me to go, and now you say no.\""},{"time":145206,"text":"And they thought about it all night."},{"time":146954,"text":"And they came into my room the next morning."},{"time":149088,"text":"They had not slept."},{"time":150588,"text":"They had been literally crying and praying and thinking,"},{"time":153104,"text":"\"Will we let our 12-year-old"},{"time":156664,"text":"participate in this march and probably have to go to jail?\""},{"time":160816,"text":"And they decided to do it."},{"time":162505,"text":"And when they came in to tell me,"},{"time":163887,"text":"I was at first elated."},{"time":165672,"text":"And then all of a sudden I began thinking about the dogs and the fire hoses,"},{"time":169604,"text":"and I got really scared, I really did."},{"time":172486,"text":"And one of the points I make to people all the time"},{"time":174588,"text":"is that sometimes when people do things that are courageous,"},{"time":177823,"text":"it doesn't really mean that they're that courageous."},{"time":180172,"text":"It simply means that they believe it's important to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183020,"text":"I wanted a better education."},{"time":184771,"text":"I did not want to have to have hand-me-down books."},{"time":188004,"text":"I wanted to know that the school I attended"},{"time":190487,"text":"not only had good teachers, but the resources we needed."},{"time":192912,"text":"And as a result of that experience,"},{"time":194588,"text":"in the middle of the week, while I was there in jail,"},{"time":196922,"text":"Dr. King came and said with our parents,"},{"time":199472,"text":"\"What you children do this day"},{"time":202437,"text":"will have an impact on children who have not been born.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":207021,"text":"I recently realized that two-thirds of Americans today"},{"time":211956,"text":"had not been born at the time of 1963."},{"time":215470,"text":"And so for them, when they hear about the Children's Crusade in Birmingham,"},{"time":218411,"text":"in many ways, if they see it on TV,"},{"time":220673,"text":"it's like our looking at the 1863 \"Lincoln\" movie:"},{"time":224087,"text":"It's history."},{"time":225521,"text":"And the real question is, what lessons did we learn?"},{"time":228494,"text":"Well amazingly, the most important for me was this:"},{"time":231386,"text":"That children can be empowered to take ownership of their education."},{"time":236686,"text":"They can be taught to be passionate"},{"time":239037,"text":"about wanting to learn and to love the idea of asking questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243578,"text":"And so it is especially significant"},{"time":246373,"text":"that the university I now lead,"},{"time":248459,"text":"the University of Maryland, Baltimore County, UMBC,"},{"time":251254,"text":"was founded the very year I went to jail with Dr. King, in 1963."},{"time":257040,"text":"And what made that institutional founding especially important"},{"time":261210,"text":"is that Maryland is the South, as you know,"},{"time":265744,"text":"and, quite frankly, it was the first university in our state"},{"time":270326,"text":"founded at a time when students of all races could go there."},{"time":274402,"text":"And so we had black and white students and others who began to attend."},{"time":277975,"text":"And it has been for 50 years an experiment."},{"time":282160,"text":"The experiment is this:"},{"time":283860,"text":"Is it possible to have institutions in our country, universities,"},{"time":287819,"text":"where people from all backgrounds can come and learn"},{"time":290756,"text":"and learn to work together and learn to become leaders"},{"time":294339,"text":"and to support each other in that experience?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":297912,"text":"Now what is especially important about that experience for me is this:"},{"time":302827,"text":"We found that we could do a lot in the arts and humanities and social sciences."},{"time":307495,"text":"And so we began to work on that, for years in the '60s."},{"time":310051,"text":"And we produced a number of people in law, all the way to the humanities."},{"time":313834,"text":"We produced great artists. Beckett is our muse."},{"time":316467,"text":"A lot of our students get into theater."},{"time":318004,"text":"It's great work."},{"time":319004,"text":"The problem that we faced was the same problem America continues to face --"},{"time":323036,"text":"that students in the sciences and engineering,"},{"time":324883,"text":"black students were not succeeding."},{"time":326994,"text":"But when I looked at the data,"},{"time":328745,"text":"what I found was that, quite frankly, students in general,"},{"time":332077,"text":"large numbers were not making it."},{"time":333700,"text":"And as a result of that,"},{"time":335618,"text":"we decided to do something that would help, first of all,"},{"time":338952,"text":"the group at the bottom, African-American students, and then Hispanic students."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343169,"text":"And Robert and Jane Meyerhoff, philanthropists, said, \"We'd like to help.\""},{"time":347500,"text":"Robert Meyerhoff said, \"Why is it that everything I see on TV about black boys,"},{"time":350953,"text":"if it's not about basketball, is not positive?"},{"time":353751,"text":"I'd like to make a difference, to do something that's positive.\""},{"time":356383,"text":"We married those ideas, and we created this Meyerhoff Scholars program."},{"time":360050,"text":"And what is significant about the program"},{"time":362119,"text":"is that we learned a number of things."},{"time":364600,"text":"And the question is this:"},{"time":365952,"text":"How is it that now we lead the country in producing African-Americans"},{"time":370417,"text":"who go on to complete Ph.D.'s in science and engineering and M.D./Ph.D.'s?"},{"time":375267,"text":"That's a big deal. Give me a hand for that. That's a big deal."},{"time":377916,"text":"That's a big deal. It really is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380151,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":382727,"text":"You see, most people don't realize"},{"time":384671,"text":"that it's not just minorities who don't do well in science and engineering."},{"time":388721,"text":"Quite frankly, you're talking about Americans."},{"time":392338,"text":"If you don't know it, while 20 percent of blacks and Hispanics"},{"time":395786,"text":"who begin with a major in science and engineering"},{"time":398121,"text":"will actually graduate in science and engineering,"},{"time":400273,"text":"only 32 percent of whites who begin with majors in those areas"},{"time":403827,"text":"actually succeed and graduate in those areas,"},{"time":406485,"text":"and only 42 percent of Asian-Americans."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408590,"text":"And so, the real question is, what is the challenge?"},{"time":411201,"text":"Well a part of it, of course, is K-12."},{"time":413588,"text":"We need to strengthen K-12."},{"time":415537,"text":"But the other part has to do with the culture"},{"time":417833,"text":"of science and engineering on our campuses."},{"time":420493,"text":"Whether you know it or not, large numbers of students with high SAT's"},{"time":424338,"text":"and large numbers of A.P. credits"},{"time":425803,"text":"who go to the most prestigious universities in our country"},{"time":428505,"text":"begin in pre-med or pre-engineering and engineering, and they end up changing their majors."},{"time":433336,"text":"And the number one reason, we find, quite frankly,"},{"time":435802,"text":"is they did not do well in first year science courses."},{"time":438752,"text":"In fact, we call first year science and engineering, typically around America,"},{"time":442535,"text":"weed-out courses or barrier courses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444669,"text":"How many of you in this audience know somebody"},{"time":446437,"text":"who started off in pre-med or engineering"},{"time":448252,"text":"and changed their major within a year or two?"},{"time":450137,"text":"It's an American challenge. Half of you in the room."},{"time":451935,"text":"I know. I know. I know."},{"time":453336,"text":"And what is interesting about that"},{"time":454994,"text":"is that so many students are smart and can do it."},{"time":457704,"text":"We need to find ways of making it happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459970,"text":"So what are the four things we did to help minority students"},{"time":462577,"text":"that now are helping students in general?"},{"time":464386,"text":"Number one: high expectations."},{"time":466253,"text":"It takes an understanding of the academic preparation of students --"},{"time":470758,"text":"their grades, the rigor of the course work,"},{"time":473102,"text":"their test-taking skills, their attitude,"},{"time":475553,"text":"the fire in their belly, the passion for the work, to make it."},{"time":478278,"text":"And so doing things to help students prepare to be in that position, very important."},{"time":482519,"text":"But equally important, it takes an understanding that it's hard work that makes the difference."},{"time":487618,"text":"I don't care how smart you are or how smart you think you are."},{"time":490136,"text":"Smart simply means you're ready to learn."},{"time":492503,"text":"You're excited about learning and you want to ask good questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495745,"text":"I. I. Rabi, a Nobel laureate, said that when he was growing up in New York,"},{"time":500032,"text":"all of his friends' parents would ask them"},{"time":502578,"text":"\"What did you learn in school?\" at the end of a day."},{"time":505220,"text":"And he said, in contrast, his Jewish mother would say,"},{"time":508757,"text":"\"Izzy, did you ask a good question today?\""},{"time":511819,"text":"And so high expectations have to do with curiosity"},{"time":514518,"text":"and encouraging young people to be curious."},{"time":517036,"text":"And as a result of those high expectations,"},{"time":518552,"text":"we began to find students we wanted to work with"},{"time":521219,"text":"to see what could we do to help them,"},{"time":522912,"text":"not simply to survive in science and engineering,"},{"time":525452,"text":"but to become the very best, to excel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528386,"text":"Interestingly enough, an example:"},{"time":530203,"text":"One young man who earned a C in the first course and wanted to go on to med school,"},{"time":535105,"text":"we said, \"We need to have you retake the course,"},{"time":537220,"text":"because you need a strong foundation if you're going to move to the next level.\""},{"time":541004,"text":"Every foundation makes the difference in the next level."},{"time":544035,"text":"He retook the course."},{"time":545176,"text":"That young man went on to graduate from UMBC,"},{"time":547605,"text":"to become the first black to get the M.D./Ph.D. from the University of Pennsylvania."},{"time":551802,"text":"He now works at Harvard."},{"time":553008,"text":"Nice story. Give him a hand for that too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555455,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":557886,"text":"Secondly, it's not about test scores only."},{"time":560381,"text":"Test scores are important, but they're not the most important thing."},{"time":562370,"text":"One young woman had great grades, but test scores were not as high."},{"time":565415,"text":"But she had a factor that was very important."},{"time":567464,"text":"She never missed a day of school, K-12."},{"time":570712,"text":"There was fire in that belly."},{"time":572133,"text":"That young woman went on, and she is today with an M.D./Ph.D. from Hopkins."},{"time":576257,"text":"She's on the faculty, tenure track in psychiatry, Ph.D. in neuroscience."},{"time":580475,"text":"She and her adviser have a patent on a second use of Viagra for diabetes patients."},{"time":585286,"text":"Big hand for her. Big hand for her."},{"time":587771,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":589157,"text":"And so high expectations, very important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":591677,"text":"Secondly, the idea of building community among the students."},{"time":594536,"text":"You all know that so often in science and engineering"},{"time":597303,"text":"we tend to think cutthroat."},{"time":598994,"text":"Students are not taught to work in groups."},{"time":601310,"text":"And that's what we work to do with that group"},{"time":603202,"text":"to get them to understand each other,"},{"time":604705,"text":"to build trust among them, to support each other,"},{"time":607328,"text":"to learn how to ask good questions,"},{"time":609037,"text":"but also to learn how to explain concepts with clarity."},{"time":612524,"text":"As you know, it's one thing to earn an A yourself,"},{"time":614787,"text":"it's another thing to help someone else do well."},{"time":616912,"text":"And so to feel that sense of responsibility makes all the difference in the world."},{"time":620827,"text":"So building community among those students, very important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":623774,"text":"Third, the idea of, it takes researchers to produce researchers."},{"time":628578,"text":"Whether you're talking about artists producing artists"},{"time":631107,"text":"or you're talking about people getting into the social sciences,"},{"time":634022,"text":"whatever the discipline -- and especially in science and engineering, as in art, for example --"},{"time":638869,"text":"you need scientists to pull the students into the work."},{"time":641672,"text":"And so our students are working in labs regularly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644412,"text":"And one great example that you'll appreciate:"},{"time":646786,"text":"During a snowstorm in Baltimore several years ago,"},{"time":649846,"text":"the guy on our campus with this Howard Hughes Medical Institute grant"},{"time":653466,"text":"literally came back to work in his lab after several days,"},{"time":657890,"text":"and all these students had refused to leave the lab."},{"time":661183,"text":"They had food they had packed out."},{"time":663267,"text":"They were in the lab working,"},{"time":664582,"text":"and they saw the work, not as schoolwork, but as their lives."},{"time":668583,"text":"They knew they were working on AIDS research."},{"time":670495,"text":"They were looking at this amazing protein design."},{"time":673703,"text":"And what was interesting was each one of them focused on that work."},{"time":678036,"text":"And he said, \"It doesn't get any better than that.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":680202,"text":"And then finally, if you've got the community"},{"time":682287,"text":"and you've got the high expectations and you've got researchers producing researchers,"},{"time":685900,"text":"you have to have people who are willing as faculty"},{"time":688788,"text":"to get involved with those students, even in the classroom."},{"time":691851,"text":"I'll never forget a faculty member calling the staff and saying,"},{"time":694299,"text":"\"I've got this young man in class, a young black guy,"},{"time":696744,"text":"and he seems like he's just not excited about the work."},{"time":699784,"text":"He's not taking notes. We need to talk to him.\""},{"time":702019,"text":"What was significant was that the faculty member was observing every student"},{"time":705891,"text":"to understand who was really involved and who was not"},{"time":708807,"text":"and was saying, \"Let me see how I can work with them."},{"time":711174,"text":"Let me get the staff to help me out.\""},{"time":712411,"text":"It was that connecting."},{"time":713563,"text":"That young man today is actually a faculty member M.D./Ph.D. in neuroengineering at Duke."},{"time":718495,"text":"Give him a big hand for that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719707,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":721703,"text":"And so the significance is that we have now developed this model"},{"time":726523,"text":"that is helping us, not only finally with evaluation, assessing what works."},{"time":730688,"text":"And what we learned was that we needed to think about redesigning courses."},{"time":734120,"text":"And so we redesigned chemistry, we redesigned physics."},{"time":736661,"text":"But now we are looking at redesigning the humanities and social sciences."},{"time":740322,"text":"Because so many students are bored in class."},{"time":742869,"text":"Do you know that?"},{"time":744049,"text":"Many students, K-12 and in universities,"},{"time":745995,"text":"don't want to just sit there and listen to somebody talk."},{"time":748500,"text":"They need to be engaged."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749870,"text":"And so we have done -- if you look at our website at the Chemistry Discovery Center,"},{"time":753320,"text":"you'll see people coming from all over the country"},{"time":755285,"text":"to look at how we are redesigning courses,"},{"time":757864,"text":"having an emphasis on collaboration, use of technology,"},{"time":761355,"text":"using problems out of our biotech companies on our campus,"},{"time":764585,"text":"and not giving students the theories,"},{"time":766615,"text":"but having them struggle with those theories."},{"time":768847,"text":"And it's working so well that throughout our university system in Maryland,"},{"time":772506,"text":"more and more courses are being redesigned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774547,"text":"It's called academic innovation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776381,"text":"And what does all of that mean?"},{"time":777586,"text":"It means that now, not just in science and engineering,"},{"time":780429,"text":"we now have programs in the arts, in the humanities, in the social sciences,"},{"time":784537,"text":"in teacher education, even particularly for women in I.T."},{"time":789129,"text":"If you don't know it, there's been a 79-percent decline"},{"time":793216,"text":"in the number of women majoring in computer science just since 2000."},{"time":797334,"text":"And what I'm saying is that what will make the difference"},{"time":800647,"text":"will be building community among students,"},{"time":803202,"text":"telling young women, young minority students and students in general,"},{"time":806198,"text":"you can do this work."},{"time":807447,"text":"And most important, giving them a chance to build that community"},{"time":810717,"text":"with faculty pulling them into the work"},{"time":812880,"text":"and our assessing what works and what does not work."},{"time":815398,"text":"Most important, if a student has a sense of self,"},{"time":819246,"text":"it is amazing how the dreams and the values"},{"time":822130,"text":"can make all the difference in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":824119,"text":"When I was a 12-year-old child in the jail in Birmingham,"},{"time":827749,"text":"I kept thinking, \"I wonder what my future could be.\""},{"time":831013,"text":"I had no idea that it was possible for this little black boy in Birmingham"},{"time":836798,"text":"to one day be president of a university that has students from 150 countries,"},{"time":841763,"text":"where students are not there just to survive,"},{"time":844119,"text":"where they love learning, where they enjoy being the best,"},{"time":848120,"text":"where they will one day change the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850661,"text":"Aristotle said, \"Excellence is never an accident."},{"time":854036,"text":"It is the result of high intention, sincere effort and intelligent execution."},{"time":860031,"text":"It represents the wisest option among many alternatives.\""},{"time":863963,"text":"And then he said something that gives me goosebumps."},{"time":866297,"text":"He said, \"Choice, not chance, determines your destiny.\""},{"time":871944,"text":"Choice, not chance, determines your destiny, dreams and values."}]},{"cues":[{"time":879506,"text":"Thank you all very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":881440,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}